	   <tr><td colspan=2>Near as I've ever been able to tell, 4 AGI gets you one point of AC.&nbsp;&nbsp;Don't know if level affects that - haven't checked it in a while.  The key thing to consider is that it takes a lot of Agi to get a little AC - and even if you burn 15 stat points on Agi you're only getting 4 AC for it.  Considering that at high levels there seems to be a multiplying effect when you equip AC gear (If I equip a AC 7 piece, my AC goes up 10 or 11 - never saw an explanation for it though) the 3 or 4 AC you get from skill points doesn't seem to be a good return on investment here.<br><br>Keyeluke <br>Monk of the Silent Fist, 45th Circle <br>Strange Brew <br>Druzzil Ro <br><br>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a><br>Dripsy - <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=227922</a></td></tr>
