	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you're levelling *very* quickly (regardless of reason), Mend will lag -- it's far and away the slowest skill to raise, simply due to the 6 minute refresh time.&nbsp;&nbsp;At higher levels, even if you level slowly, Mend will fall behind.<br><br>Just make sure you mash it every time it refreshes, unless you're in a battle without a healer and can't take a chance on a fail.  There's really nothing else you can do about it.<br>&nbsp;<br>Osano<br>Level 44 Human Monk<br>Tholuxe-Paells</td></tr>
